@startuml
title Domain Model - Learning Management System (LMS)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
left to right direction

' ==============================
' Description Note (Fixed Syntax)
' ==============================
note as N1
Domain Model Description:

The domain model represents the core entities and relationships 
within the Learning Management System (LMS). The abstract User 
class defines shared attributes and is specialized into Student 
and Instructor through inheritance. Students enroll in courses 
via Enrollment and submit assignments through Submission. 
Instructors teach courses, create assignments, assign grades, 
and send notifications. Courses organize materials using 
Modules and ContentItems. Each assignment may have multiple 
submissions, and each submission may result in a Grade. 
Notifications support communication between instructors and students.
end note

' ==============================
' Core Users
' ==============================
abstract class User {
  userId : UUID
  fullName : String
  email : String
  status : String
}

class Student {
  studentNumber : String
  program : String
}

class Instructor {
  employeeId : String
  officeHours : String
}

User <|-- Student
User <|-- Instructor

' ==============================
' Course Structure
' ==============================
class Course {
  courseId : String
  title : String
  term : String
}

class Module {
  moduleId : String
  title : String
  orderIndex : int
}

class ContentItem {
  contentId : String
  title : String
  type : String
  url : String
}

Course "1" *-- "0..*" Module
Module "1" *-- "0..*" ContentItem

' ==============================
' Enrollment
' ==============================
class Enrollment {
  enrollmentId : UUID
  enrolledOn : Date
  status : String
}

Student "1" -- "0..*" Enrollment
Course  "1" -- "0..*" Enrollment

' ==============================
' Assignments & Submissions
' ==============================
class Assignment {
  assignmentId : UUID
  title : String
  dueDate : DateTime
  maxPoints : int
}

class Submission {
  submissionId : UUID
  submittedAt : DateTime
  fileUrl : String
  status : String
}

class Grade {
  gradeId : UUID
  score : float
  feedback : String
  gradedAt : DateTime
}

Course "1" *-- "0..*" Assignment
Assignment "1" -- "0..*" Submission
Student "1" -- "0..*" Submission
Submission "0..1" -- "1" Grade
Instructor "1" -- "0..*" Grade

' ==============================
' Notifications
' ==============================
class Notification {
  notificationId : UUID
  message : String
  createdAt : DateTime
  channel : String
}

Instructor "1" -- "0..*" Notification
Course "1" -- "0..*" Notification
Student "0..*" -- "0..*" Notification

@enduml
